description.content:

With extensive expertise in Bubble.io development, I specialize in crafting customized, user-friendly apps and websites on the Bubble.io platform. I can make a booking system app, message and notification system, or any other project listed below, I have the expertise to make it happen. Let's turn your idea into reality on the Bubble.io platform!


You can Order:

  • Booking system app
  • Message and notification system
  • Video streaming integration
  • Signup / Login
  • Education, Health, Real State others
  • Questionnaires, Surveys, Quizzes
  • CRM's
  • Calendar & scheduling
  • Job board app
  • Admin Panels
  • SPA (single-page application)
  • ChatGPT API and any third-party integrations
  • Payment gateways (Stripe, Paypal & others)
  • Social Logins

and more!


Why Me?

  • 5+ Years Experience as a No-Code Bubble App Developer
  • High-Quality Work
  • Available 24/7 for all of your queries
  • Friendly Attitude
  • Free support after work completion.


Let's collaborate on your Bubble app or website project and unlock its full potential.

Contact me now to discuss your project details.


Regards

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Bubble.io?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Bubble.io is a powerful no-code platform that empowers users to create web applications without writing code. It offers a range of features and functionalities to build sophisticated apps and websites efficiently.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate third-party services into my Bubble.io app?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! I can seamlessly integrate various third-party services and APls to enhance the functionality of your Bubble.io app, including payment gateways, social media logins, and more.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer ongoing support and maintenance for Bubble.io apps?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide comprehensive support and maintenance services to ensure that your Bubble.io app remains secure, and up-to-date, and performs optimally even after the project completion. My goal is to ensure the long-term success of your app.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is Bubble good for SEO?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Bubble offers a range of built-in SEO settings, providing a powerful way to enhance the visibility and search ability of your app.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is bubble a safe site?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Bubble complies with the SOC 2 Type II standard for security and offers a GDPR-compliant data processing agreement (DPA).

I had the pleasure of working with Adul Basit, and I can confidently say he exceeded my expectations in every way. 

From the very beginning, his professionalism, expertise, and commitment to delivering high-quality work stood out.

He designed and developed my blog with precision, ensuring a visually stunning, user-friendly, and fully functional website. 

The final result was beyond what I had expected a sleek, responsive, and well-structured website that perfectly aligns with my brand. 

Looking forward to working with him on future projects!

seller_response.comment: Thank you so much for your kind words! It was truly a pleasure working with you. I'm glad I could help bring your vision to life with a website that aligns with your brand. Your feedback means a lot to me, and Im excited to collaborate again on future projects. Wishing you continued success with your blog!

reviews.comment:
Mixed Experience Good Design, But Project Expectations Not Met

The freelancer delivered a solid Figma design, which met expectations. However, there were misalignments in project expectations and an extended timeline beyond what was initially discussed. Despite clearly defined milestones and agreements, adjustments were made after the design phase that did not align with the original scope of work.

While I appreciate the design work, the overall experience was frustrating due to the lack of clarity in project execution. Communication and adherence to initial agreements could have been better. If working with this freelancer, I recommend ensuring that all expectations are clearly outlined.

seller_response.comment: I had said that I would provide the budget after the design phase, but they asked to cancel the order. They hadn't extended the timeline; they just mentioned that the changes to your scope are more significant now. The previous scope was fine as it was. Overall, it has been a bad experience with this buyer, and I do not recommend working with them.
